Pick a pizza establishment.
Review menu to select pizza options.
Call selected establishment to place order.
Provide payment to establishment for order.
Await arrival of your order.    
Eat food. 

If you enjoyed, follow these following steps to leave a review. 
Go to Yelp. 
Search for the pizza establishment you ordered from. 
Create an account so that you can leave a review. 
Return to their page, and provide your review on the food. 
Submit. 